description: Returns a list of summaries describing EnabledBaseline resources. You can filter the list by the corresponding Baseline or Target of the EnabledBaseline resources. For usage examples, see the Amazon Web Services Control Tower User Guide.

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: A filter applied on the ListEnabledBaseline operation. Allowed filters are baselineIdentifiers and targetIdentifiers. The filter can be applied for either, or both. baselineIdentifiers (list) --- Identifiers for the Baseline objects returned as part of the filter operation. (string) --- parentIdentifiers (list) --- An optional filter that sets up a list of parentIdentifiers to filter the results of the ListEnabledBaseline output. (string) --- targetIdentifiers (list) --- Identifiers for the targets of the Baseline filter operation. (string) ---

nested_params.name: baselineIdentifiers
nested_params.description: Identifiers for the Baseline objects returned as part of the filter operation.

nested_params.name: parentIdentifiers
nested_params.description: An optional filter that sets up a list of parentIdentifiers to filter the results of the ListEnabledBaseline output.

nested_params.name: targetIdentifiers
nested_params.description: Identifiers for the targets of the Baseline filter operation.

nested_items.name: enabledBaselines

nested_items.name: arn

nested_items.name: baselineIdentifier
nested_items.description: The specific baseline that is enabled as part of the EnabledBaseline resource.

nested_items.name: baselineVersion
nested_items.description: The enabled version of the baseline.

nested_items.name: parentIdentifier
nested_items.description: An ARN that represents an object returned by ListEnabledBaseline, to describe an enabled baseline.

nested_items.name: statusSummary
nested_items.description: The deployment summary of an EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline resource.

nested_items.name: lastOperationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The last operation identifier for the enabled resource.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The deployment status of the enabled resource.
SUCCEEDED: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration was deployed successfully.
UNDER_CHANGE: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration is changing.
FAILED: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration failed to deploy.

nested_items.name: targetIdentifier
nested_items.description: The target upon which the baseline is enabled.
